    "id": "e23d9d2a-d481-48b9-b998-3f5becb12b26",
    "content": "Sprint F1 completed for ZooCode Fork. F1.1: Decompiled extension.js (15MB) — documented agent loop (presentAssistantMessage dispatch), tool system (Ui base class with read_file/write_to_file/apply_diff/execute_command), MCP client (McpHub with getServers/callTool/readResource), activation (Z_l function). Output: ARCHITECTURE.md with 5 hook points. F1.2: Set up esbuild build pipeline (esbuild.config.js, tsconfig.json, package.json) that bundles src/extension.ts → dist/extension.js. F1.3: Created .vscode/launch.json for Extension Host debugging with preLaunchTask. F1.4: Ported all 31 agents from .roomodes into src/agents.ts with typed AgentDefinition interface. F1.5: npm install, npm run build verified, git init, force-pushed to github.com/Jpkoech30/zoocode-fork.git. All F1 tasks DONE.",
